import { Container, Form, Input } from "semantic-ui-react";

export function Login() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Form>
                <Form.Field>
                    <label>Username/Email</label>
                    <input placeholder="Username/Email"/>
                </Form.Field>
                <Form.Field>
                    <label>Username/Email</label>
                    <input placeholder="Password" />
                </Form.Field>
            </Form>
        </Container>
    )
}
